translation: 迷子になっててごめんよー{#Name="ミハイル"}
source: 迷子になっててごめんよー{#Name="ミハイル"}

translation: 石像が持っているランタンの向いてる方向に橋があるな……{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: 石像が持っているランタンの向いてる方向に橋があるな……{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: ゼロ！ゼロ！川の中にドラゴンが居るよ！{#Name="ミハイル"}
source: ゼロ！ゼロ！川の中にドラゴンが居るよ！{#Name="ミハイル"}

translation: ミハイル……それはキミの顔だ{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: ミハイル……それはキミの顔だ{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: なあんだ。じゃあ安心……{#Name="ミハイル"}
source: なあんだ。じゃあ安心……{#Name="ミハイル"}

translation: うわーっ！ゼローッ！{#Name="ミハイル"}
source: うわーっ！ゼローッ！{#Name="ミハイル"}

translation: 流されたミハイルについての会話{#Name="デカード"}
source: 流されたミハイルについての会話{#Name="デカード"}

translation: ここが迷いの森である事を伝えられる。{#Name="オクタ"}
source: ここが迷いの森である事を伝えられる。{#Name="オクタ"}

translation: 人形の向きに何かヒントがある的な台詞{#Name="オクタ"}
source: 人形の向きに何かヒントがある的な台詞{#Name="オクタ"}

translation: クソッ！どうなってるんだこの霧は！{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: クソッ！どうなってるんだこの霧は！{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: あの気持ち悪い人形の示す方向に行かないとダメっぽいな{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: あの気持ち悪い人形の示す方向に行かないとダメっぽいな{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: クソッ！ようやく出られた。忌々しい森がっ！{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: クソッ！ようやく出られた。忌々しい森がっ！{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: 出られても出られなくても『クソッ』って言うんだね{#Name="ディト"}
source: 出られても出られなくても『クソッ』って言うんだね{#Name="ディト"}

translation: クソッ！ようやく出られた。忌々しい森がっ！{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: クソッ！ようやく出られた。忌々しい森がっ！{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: 出られても出られなくても『クソッ』って言うのですね（仮）{#Name="デカート"}
source: 出られても出られなくても『クソッ』って言うのですね（仮）{#Name="デカート"}

translation: クソッ！ようやく出られた。忌々しい森がっ！{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: クソッ！ようやく出られた。忌々しい森がっ！{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: 出られても出られなくても『クソッ』っと言うのですじゃな（仮）{#Name="オクタ"}
source: 出られても出られなくても『クソッ』っと言うのですじゃな（仮）{#Name="オクタ"}

translation: 森でストレスまみれのゼロの台詞{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: 森でストレスまみれのゼロの台詞{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: 楽しませてくれよ{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: 楽しませてくれよ{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: ランドマークツリーを見上げながら、台詞{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: ランドマークツリーを見上げながら、台詞{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: クソッ！ここは入口じゃないかっ！{#Name="ゼロ"}
source: クソッ！ここは入口じゃないかっ！{#Name="ゼロ"}

translation: Be careful! Visibility is poor!{#Name="Soldier A"}
source: Be careful! Visibility is poor!{#Name="Soldier A"}

translation: Dammit, how am I supposed to aim in all this fog!?{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: Dammit, how am I supposed to aim in all this fog!?{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Our foes have it just as bad. Stay focused!{#Name="Soldier E"}
source: Our foes have it just as bad. Stay focused!{#Name="Soldier E"}

translation: I'm gonna die here... And I'll never fulfill my dream of sleeping with Lady Three!{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: I'm gonna die here... And I'll never fulfill my dream of sleeping with Lady Three!{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: What? This is a hell of a time to come out, man!{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: What? This is a hell of a time to come out, man!{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: There! Over on the right!{#Name="Soldier F"}
source: There! Over on the right!{#Name="Soldier F"}

translation: I'm not goin' down yet!{#Name="Soldier B"}
source: I'm not goin' down yet!{#Name="Soldier B"}

translation: Quit messing around with me, Zero, or I'll stab your demon ass!{#Name="Soldier C"}
source: Quit messing around with me, Zero, or I'll stab your demon ass!{#Name="Soldier C"}

translation: Why do you get lost all the damn time?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Why do you get lost all the damn time?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I dunno what happened! I thought I was{LF}flying next to you like always!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: I dunno what happened! I thought I was{LF}flying next to you like always!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Aww, that's not true! That's not true at all!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Aww, that's not true! That's not true at all!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: It IS true! It IS true at all!{#Name="Dito"}
source: It IS true! It IS true at all!{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Looks like there's a bridge where{LF}the statue is pointing its lantern.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Looks like there's a bridge where{LF}the statue is pointing its lantern.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Zero! Zero! There's a dragon in the river!{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Zero! Zero! There's a dragon in the river!{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Ohhhh... Well, never mind th— Huh!?{#Name="Mikhail"}
source: Ohhhh... Well, never mind th— Huh!?{#Name="Mikhail"}

translation: Er, yes, but what I was actually asking is—{#Name="Decadus"}
source: Er, yes, but what I was actually asking is—{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: Look, I don't know. Maybe some crazy{LF}cat lady'll adopt him, okay?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Look, I don't know. Maybe some crazy{LF}cat lady'll adopt him, okay?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Lady Three liked to call this area the Lost Forest.{#Name="Octa"}
source: Lady Three liked to call this area the Lost Forest.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: So is there a way out, or what?{#Name="Dito"}
source: So is there a way out, or what?{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Oh ho! Sadly, I'm not good for much besides{LF}a bit of the old rump and tickle.{#Name="Octa"}
source: Oh ho! Sadly, I'm not good for much besides{LF}a bit of the old rump and tickle.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: That's not really something to brag about.{#Name="Dito"}
source: That's not really something to brag about.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Though, when I was playing with the faeries,{LF}I do believe I heard something about minding{LF}the direction of the dolls...{#Name="Octa"}
source: Though, when I was playing with the faeries,{LF}I do believe I heard something about minding{LF}the direction of the dolls...{#Name="Octa"}

translation: ...Please don't tell me you were bonking faeries. {#Name="Zero"}
source: ...Please don't tell me you were bonking faeries. {#Name="Zero"}

translation: Dammit! This fog is really{LF}starting to piss me off!{#Name="Zero"}
source: Dammit! This fog is really{LF}starting to piss me off!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: I guess we've no choice but to{LF}follow those creepy-ass dolls.{#Name="Zero"}
source: I guess we've no choice but to{LF}follow those creepy-ass dolls.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Ugh, we're finally free of this stupid shithole.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Ugh, we're finally free of this stupid shithole.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: You know, for an Intoner, you sure do use{LF}a lot of colorful language.{#Name="Dito"}
source: You know, for an Intoner, you sure do use{LF}a lot of colorful language.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: What do you want? That fucking forest pissed me off!{#Name="Zero"}
source: What do you want? That fucking forest pissed me off!{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Ah, yes. There's a reason it's known as{LF}"the forest that breaks minds."{#Name="Octa"}
source: Ah, yes. There's a reason it's known as{LF}"the forest that breaks minds."{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Yeah, well, Z's mind was already broken.{LF}Maybe that just put it back together.{#Name="Dito"}
source: Yeah, well, Z's mind was already broken.{LF}Maybe that just put it back together.{#Name="Dito"}

translation: Hey, funny guy! Let's see how funny you are{LF}with a sword up your ass.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Hey, funny guy! Let's see how funny you are{LF}with a sword up your ass.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Um, Octa? What are you doing?{#Name="Zero"}
source: Um, Octa? What are you doing?{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Oh, nothing, my lady. Nothing of importance...{#Name="Octa"}
source: Oh, nothing, my lady. Nothing of importance...{#Name="Octa"}

translation: He was measuring the length of...{LF}Well, he was measuring...something.{#Name="Decadus"}
source: He was measuring the length of...{LF}Well, he was measuring...something.{#Name="Decadus"}

translation: I'm merely a scientist collecting data{LF}on my finest assets, my lady.{#Name="Octa"}
source: I'm merely a scientist collecting data{LF}on my finest assets, my lady.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: I mean, what's the point of owning art{LF}if you don't view it once in a while?{#Name="Octa"}
source: I mean, what's the point of owning art{LF}if you don't view it once in a while?{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Nice. This should be fun. I haven't had{LF}something meaty to rip into in forever.{#Name="Zero"}
source: Nice. This should be fun. I haven't had{LF}something meaty to rip into in forever.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: There's something weird about this tree.{#Name="Zero"}
source: There's something weird about this tree.{#Name="Zero"}

translation: Well, as I said before, it is the shrine of Lady Three.{#Name="Octa"}
source: Well, as I said before, it is the shrine of Lady Three.{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Let's thrust ourselves inside, shall we?{#Name="Octa"}
source: Let's thrust ourselves inside, shall we?{#Name="Octa"}

translation: Guided by the disciple Octa,{LF}the group tracked down the shrine where Three was hiding.{#Name="Accord"}
source: Guided by the disciple Octa,{LF}the group tracked down the shrine where Three was hiding.{#Name="Accord"}

translation: Soon, Zero found herself before the Lost Forest,{#Name="Accord"}
source: Soon, Zero found herself before the Lost Forest,{#Name="Accord"}

translation: a foreboding region from which no one has escaped.{#Name="Accord"}
source: a foreboding region from which no one has escaped.{#Name="Accord"}
